      com.xtructure.xutil.id.XValId<V>
Type Parameters:
V - the type of value identified.
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<XId>
public class XValId<V>
extends XId

The Class XValId. XValId instances identify values by name and type. Unlike XId , XValId doesn't support instance numbers.

Author:
Luis Guimbarda
